name: Inter-dimensional Ranger Training Program
description:
You are aspiring to become an Inter-dimensional Ranger. As you attend your first day of training, you don't receive your inter-dimensional gadgets. And your trainer isn't the best listener in the dimensions. As you go into training unarmed you have to use unconventional means to finish it. Play the same level again and again with a twist.

PS: No audio! Apologies!
